---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import MobileTease from '../../../components/MobileTease.astro';
const APP_URL = 'https://dev.audioask.ai';
---

<Layout
  title="Automate podcast processing — Audioask"
  description="Set up automation on any channel: every new episode is automatically transcribed, analyzed by AI, and delivered to your library or inbox."
  activePage="features"
  lang="en"
  alternatePath="/fonctionnalites/automatiser"
>
<Fragment slot="head">
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
    "itemListElement": [
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://www.audioask.ai/en" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Features", "item": "https://www.audioask.ai/en/features" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 3, "name": "Automate", "item": "https://www.audioask.ai/en/features/automate" }
    ]
  })} />
</Fragment>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero dotbg">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-copy">
        <div class="page-intro" style="margin-bottom: 24px;">Feature 03 · Automate</div>
        <h1>Configure once.<br><span class="em-serif">Receive automatically</span> with every new episode.</h1>
        <p class="lede">
          Pick a channel, save a prompt, choose where to deliver: every new episode triggers your workflow without any intervention.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-ctas">
          <a class="btn btn-primary lg" href={`${APP_URL}/signup`}>Set up my first automation <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
          <a class="btn lg" href="/en/pricing">See plans</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 3-phase flow visual -->
      <div class="auto-flow" style="margin-top: 60px;">
        <div class="auto-step">
          <div class="eyebrow"><span style="color: var(--accent);">01</span> · Channel</div>
          <h4 style="margin-top: 6px; font-size: 17px;">Pick a channel</h4>
          <div style="margin-top: 8px; padding: 12px 14px; background: var(--cream-2); border-radius: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;">
            <img src="/assets/pod-acquired.jpg" alt="Acquired" style="width: 36px; height: 36px; border-radius: 8px; object-fit: cover; flex-shrink: 0;">
            <div style="flex: 1; min-width: 0;">
              <div style="font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600;">Acquired</div>
              <div style="font-size: 11px; color: var(--ink-3);">142 episodes</div>
            </div>
            <span class="chip accent" style="font-size: 10px; height: 22px; padding: 0 8px;">✓</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="auto-arrow">→</div>

        <div class="auto-step">
          <div class="eyebrow"><span style="color: var(--accent);">02</span> · Prompt</div>
          <h4 style="margin-top: 6px; font-size: 17px;">Define an AI prompt</h4>
          <div style="margin-top: 8px; padding: 12px 14px; background: var(--cream-2); border-radius: 10px; font-size: 12.5px; color: var(--ink-2); line-height: 1.4; font-family: var(--mono);">
            Summarize this episode in 5<br>actionable points for a client brief.
          </div>
          <div style="margin-top: 8px; font-size: 11px; color: var(--ink-3); font-family: var(--mono); letter-spacing: 0.05em;">OR NONE — TRANSCRIPTION ONLY</div>
        </div>

        <div class="auto-arrow">→</div>

        <div class="auto-step">
          <div class="eyebrow"><span style="color: var(--accent);">03</span> · Delivery</div>
          <h4 style="margin-top: 6px; font-size: 17px;">Choose delivery</h4>
          <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; margin-top: 8px;">
            <div style="padding: 10px 12px; background: var(--accent-tint); border: 1px solid var(--accent); border-radius: 8px; display: flex; gap: 8px; align-items: center; font-size: 12px; color: var(--accent-ink);"><span>✓</span> Library</div>
            <div style="padding: 10px 12px; background: var(--accent-tint); border: 1px solid var(--accent); border-radius: 8px; display: flex; gap: 8px; align-items: center; font-size: 12px; color: var(--accent-ink);"><span>✓</span> Email</div>
            <div style="padding: 10px 12px; background: var(--cream-2); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 8px; display: flex; gap: 8px; align-items: center; font-size: 12px; color: var(--ink-3);"><span>○</span> Webhook · Slack <span class="chip" style="margin-left: auto; height: 18px; padding: 0 6px; font-size: 9px; background: var(--ink); color: var(--cream); border: 0;">PRO</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
  <section class="section alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row between" style="align-items: flex-end; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 32px;">
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow"><span class="dot">●</span> How it works</div>
          <h2 style="margin-top: 16px;">A 30-second setup,<br><span class="serif-it">a workflow for the whole year.</span></h2>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-alt" style="margin-top: 48px; border-top: 0;">
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow"><span style="color: var(--accent);">01</span> · Toggle</div>
          <h3 style="margin-top: 12px;">Activate in one click from a channel.</h3>
          <p>On each followed channel, an "Auto" toggle. Enable it, configure it. Disable it whenever you want.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="demo" style="padding: 28px;">
          <div style="background: var(--paper); border-radius: 14px; border: 1px solid var(--line); padding: 22px; box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);">
            <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 16px;">
              <span style="width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 8px; background: var(--accent-tint); color: var(--accent); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
                <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"><path d="M13 2L4 14h7l-1 8 9-12h-7l1-8z"/></svg>
              </span>
              <b style="font-size: 16px;">Configure automation</b>
              <span style="margin-left: auto; color: var(--ink-3);">✕</span>
            </div>
            <div style="background: var(--cream); border-radius: 10px; padding: 12px 14px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;">
              <img src="/assets/pod-acquired.jpg" alt="Acquired" style="width: 36px; height: 36px; border-radius: 8px; object-fit: cover; flex-shrink: 0;">
              <div>
                <div style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;">Acquired</div>
                <div style="font-size: 11.5px; color: var(--ink-3);">Every new episode will be processed automatically</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div style="margin-top: 14px;">
              <div style="font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; color: var(--ink-3); letter-spacing: 0.08em; margin-bottom: 6px;">📖 AI PROMPT</div>
              <div style="background: var(--cream); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 10px; padding: 10px 14px; font-size: 13px; color: var(--ink);">— No prompt (transcription only) —</div>
            </div>
            <div style="margin-top: 14px;">
              <div style="font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; color: var(--ink-3); letter-spacing: 0.08em; margin-bottom: 6px;">RESULT DELIVERY</div>
              <div style="background: var(--accent-tint); border: 1px solid var(--accent); border-radius: 10px; padding: 10px 14px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;">
                <span style="color: var(--accent);">📚</span>
                <div style="flex: 1;">
                  <div style="font-size: 12.5px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--accent-ink);">Save to library</div>
                  <div style="font-size: 11px; color: var(--accent-deep);">Accessible in My Audioask → Results</div>
                </div>
                <span style="width: 18px; height: 18px; background: var(--accent); border-radius: 4px; color: white; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 10px;">✓</span>
              </div>
              <div style="background: var(--cream); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 10px; padding: 10px 14px; margin-top: 6px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;">
                <span style="color: var(--ink-3);">✉</span>
                <div style="flex: 1;">
                  <div style="font-size: 12.5px; font-weight: 600;">Send by email</div>
                  <div style="font-size: 11px; color: var(--ink-3);">Email as soon as transcription is ready</div>
                </div>
                <span style="width: 18px; height: 18px; background: var(--paper); border: 1px solid var(--line-2); border-radius: 4px;"></span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div style="margin-top: 18px; display: flex; gap: 10px; justify-content: flex-end;">
              <span class="chip" style="height: 32px; padding: 0 14px; font-size: 13px;">Cancel</span>
              <span class="chip accent" style="height: 32px; padding: 0 14px; font-size: 13px;">✓ Save</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-alt reverse">
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow"><span style="color: var(--accent);">02</span> · Detection</div>
          <h3 style="margin-top: 12px;">Audioask detects every new episode.</h3>
          <p>As soon as a new episode is published on the followed channel, Audioask transcribes it, applies your prompt, and delivers the result.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="demo" style="padding: 22px; aspect-ratio: auto;">
          <div style="font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; color: var(--ink-3); letter-spacing: 0.08em; margin-bottom: 12px;">AUTOMATION LOG · ACQUIRED</div>
          <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px;">
            <div style="background: var(--paper); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 10px; padding: 12px 14px; display: flex; gap: 12px; font-size: 12.5px;">
              <span style="color: var(--accent); font-size: 16px;">●</span>
              <div style="flex: 1;">
                <div style="font-weight: 600;">#119 — Nvidia: the decade</div>
                <div style="color: var(--ink-3); font-size: 11px;">Detected 12 min ago · Transcribed in 2:48 · Summary sent by email</div>
              </div>
              <span class="chip accent-soft" style="height: 22px; font-size: 10.5px; padding: 0 8px;">✓ Delivered</span>
            </div>
            <div style="background: var(--paper); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 10px; padding: 12px 14px; display: flex; gap: 12px; font-size: 12.5px;">
              <span style="color: var(--accent); font-size: 16px;">●</span>
              <div style="flex: 1;">
                <div style="font-weight: 600;">#118 — Costco</div>
                <div style="color: var(--ink-3); font-size: 11px;">Yesterday · Library + email</div>
              </div>
              <span class="chip accent-soft" style="height: 22px; font-size: 10.5px; padding: 0 8px;">✓ Delivered</span>
            </div>
            <div style="background: var(--paper); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 10px; padding: 12px 14px; display: flex; gap: 12px; font-size: 12.5px;">
              <span style="color: var(--accent); font-size: 16px;">●</span>
              <div style="flex: 1;">
                <div style="font-weight: 600;">#117 — Hermès</div>
                <div style="color: var(--ink-3); font-size: 11px;">May 10 · Library + email</div>
              </div>
              <span class="chip accent-soft" style="height: 22px; font-size: 10.5px; padding: 0 8px;">✓ Delivered</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div style="margin-top: 14px; padding: 10px 14px; background: var(--cream); border-radius: 8px; font-size: 11.5px; color: var(--ink-3); display: flex; gap: 8px; align-items: center;">
            <span style="color: var(--accent);">▶</span> Next Audioask check: in 6h.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-alt">
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow"><span style="color: var(--accent);">03</span> · Delivery</div>
          <h3 style="margin-top: 12px;">Library, email — and more with Pro.</h3>
          <p>Choose where results arrive. With Pro, unlock webhooks, Slack &amp; Teams integrations.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="demo" style="padding: 22px; aspect-ratio: auto;">
          <div style="font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; color: var(--ink-3); letter-spacing: 0.08em; margin-bottom: 14px;">AVAILABLE DESTINATIONS</div>
          <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 8px;">
            <div style="padding: 14px; background: var(--paper); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 10px; display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: center;">
              <span style="font-size: 22px;">📚</span>
              <div><div style="font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600;">Library</div><div style="font-size: 11px; color: var(--ink-3);">All plans</div></div>
            </div>
            <div style="padding: 14px; background: var(--paper); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 10px; display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: center;">
              <span style="font-size: 22px;">✉</span>
              <div><div style="font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600;">Email</div><div style="font-size: 11px; color: var(--ink-3);">All plans</div></div>
            </div>
            <div style="padding: 14px; background: var(--paper); border: 1px solid var(--accent); border-radius: 10px; display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: center;">
              <span style="color: var(--accent);">
                <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"><path d="M13 2L4 14h7l-1 8 9-12h-7l1-8z"/></svg>
              </span>
              <div><div style="font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600;">Webhook</div><div style="font-size: 11px; color: var(--accent-ink); font-family: var(--mono);">PRO</div></div>
            </div>
            <div style="padding: 14px; background: var(--paper); border: 1px solid var(--accent); border-radius: 10px; display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: center;">
              <span style="font-size: 22px;">💬</span>
              <div><div style="font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600;">Slack / Teams</div><div style="font-size: 11px; color: var(--accent-ink); font-family: var(--mono);">PRO</div></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- AI PROMO -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="feature-alt highlight">
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow">
            <span style="background: var(--accent); color: white; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 10px;">AI</span>
            {' '}Winning combination
          </div>
          <h3 style="margin-top: 12px;">Automation becomes truly powerful with AI.</h3>
          <p class="lede">Every new episode is not only transcribed but also analyzed by AI according to your prompts. Summary, key quotes, fact-checks, follow-up questions — your monitoring becomes a real conversation, not just a list.</p>
          <a class="btn btn-primary arrow" href="/en/features/ask" style="margin-top: 18px;">Discover AI analysis <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
        </div>
        <div class="demo" style="padding: 0; overflow: hidden; aspect-ratio: auto; gap: 0;">
          <!-- Email window -->
          <div style="background: var(--cream-2); padding: 10px 14px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;">
            <div style="display: flex; gap: 5px;">
              <span style="width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%; background: #f87171; opacity: .7;"></span>
              <span style="width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%; background: #fbbf24; opacity: .7;"></span>
              <span style="width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%; background: #4ade80; opacity: .7;"></span>
            </div>
            <div style="flex: 1; text-align: center; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; color: var(--ink-3); letter-spacing: 0.05em;">Inbox</div>
            <span style="font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; color: var(--accent); background: var(--accent-tint); border-radius: 10px; padding: 1px 7px;">1</span>
          </div>
          <!-- Email list item (selected) -->
          <div style="background: var(--accent-tint); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); padding: 11px 16px; display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: flex-start; cursor: default;">
            <div style="width: 34px; height: 34px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--accent); color: white; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0;">A</div>
            <div style="flex: 1; min-width: 0;">
              <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: baseline; gap: 8px;">
                <span style="font-size: 12.5px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--accent-ink);">Audioask</span>
                <span style="font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; color: var(--ink-3); white-space: nowrap;">3 min ago</span>
              </div>
              <div style="font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--accent-ink); margin-top: 2px;">Acquired #189 — AI summary ready</div>
              <div style="font-size: 11px; color: var(--accent-deep); white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; margin-top: 2px;">Your analysis of the OpenAI episode is available…</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Email body -->
          <div style="padding: 16px 18px; background: var(--paper);">
            <div style="padding-bottom: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);">
              <div style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink);">Acquired · #189 — OpenAI</div>
              <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 4px 10px; margin-top: 5px; font-size: 11px; color: var(--ink-3);">
                <span>From: <span style="color: var(--ink-2);">noreply@audioask.ai</span></span>
                <span>·</span>
                <span>To: <span style="color: var(--ink-2);">you</span></span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div style="font-size: 12.5px; color: var(--ink-2); margin-bottom: 12px;">
              <strong style="color: var(--ink);">Key points:</strong>
              <div style="margin-top: 6px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 5px;">
                <div style="display: flex; gap: 7px;"><span style="color: var(--accent); font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0;">1.</span><span>Altman rejoins the board in March 2024</span></div>
                <div style="display: flex; gap: 7px;"><span style="color: var(--accent); font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0;">2.</span><span>Valuation: $157 billion</span></div>
                <div style="display: flex; gap: 7px;"><span style="color: var(--accent); font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0;">3.</span><span>GPT-5 in secret preparation</span></div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div style="font-size: 11.5px; font-style: italic; color: var(--accent-ink); border-left: 2px solid var(--accent); padding-left: 8px;">"The difference between us and others is…" — 42:17</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <MobileTease lang="en" />

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="section alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="center" style="max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <div class="eyebrow center" style="justify-content: center; display: inline-flex;"><span class="dot">●</span> FAQ</div>
        <h2 style="margin-top: 16px;">Questions about <span class="serif-it">automation.</span></h2>
      </div>
      <div class="faq">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <span>How many automations can I have?</span><span class="plus">+</span>
          <div class="faq-answer">Premium plan: 1 automated channel. Pro plan: unlimited channels. On the free plan, automation is not available, but you can manually analyze any episode.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <span>What happens if I disable an automation?</span><span class="plus">+</span>
          <div class="faq-answer">Disabling an automation immediately stops monitoring the channel. The history of previous analyses remains available in your library. You can re-enable the automation at any time.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <span>Does Audioask consume my credits on each automated episode?</span><span class="plus">+</span>
          <div class="faq-answer">Yes, each automatically processed episode consumes transcription credits (and AI prompt credits if you configured one). You will receive a notification before your credits run out.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <span>Can I change the prompt on an existing automation?</span><span class="plus">+</span>
          <div class="faq-answer">Yes, you can change the prompt on an automation at any time. The change applies to the next detected episodes. Previously completed analyses are not modified.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <span>How long between publication and delivery?</span><span class="plus">+</span>
          <div class="faq-answer">Audioask monitors RSS feeds every hour. Generally, a new episode is detected within the hour following publication, then automatically transcribed and analyzed. Delivery happens within minutes of processing completing.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section dark cta-final">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Set up your first automation<br><span class="em-serif">in under a minute.</span></h2>
      <p class="lede" style="margin: 0 auto 36px; max-width: 50ch; color: var(--night-text-2);">
        1 automated channel included in the Premium plan. Unlimited with Pro.
      </p>
      <a class="btn btn-primary lg" href={`${APP_URL}/signup`} style="height: 56px; font-size: 16px; padding: 0 28px;">Configure now <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<script>
document.querySelectorAll<HTMLElement>('.faq-item').forEach(item => {
  item.addEventListener('click', () => {
    const wasOpen = item.classList.contains('open');
    document.querySelectorAll('.faq-item').forEach(i => i.classList.remove('open'));
    if (!wasOpen) item.classList.add('open');
  });
});
</script>
